      "text": "The user is asking me to start up/build something they mentioned earlier in the conversation. Looking at the context, they were discussing a \"Score View\" feature for ProLector - a pronunciation tool that makes English prosody visible. They want me to build it and try it out.\n\nBut wait - I don't have the full context of what was discussed before. I can see from the conversation snippet that they were talking about:\n- A speech notation system (ProLector Visual Prosody)\n- Music notation parallels\n- A \"Score View\" feature idea\n- Lampariello's method for English pronunciation\n\nThe user says \"pls start this up now that is built is somewhere on my pc and id like to try it\" - this implies something was built previously and they want to see it running.",
